headline: Eaton Unveils Next-generation Architecture to Advance 800 VDC Power Infrastructure for AI Factories
summary: CLEVELAND, October 13, 2025--Intelligent power management company Eaton today announced the delivery of a new reference architecture designed to accelerate the adoption of 800 VDC power in artificial intelligence (AI) data centers.
